# Candy Blast — stable v1

`popblast` is tagged `stable: 'v1'` in `src/platform/catalog.ts`. See `STABLE.md`.

## Do not change

Unless the user **explicitly authorizes** changes to Candy Blast:

- Do not edit files under `src/games/popblast/` or `games/popblast/`
- Do not change match detection, candy movement, physics, game logic, level progression, difficulty, power-up mechanics, backend, or tournament integration
- Do not change premium presentation (UI, graphics, audio, effects, HUD, menus, animations) without authorization

## Frozen scope

- `src/games/popblast/main.ts` — match-3 gameplay + presentation hooks
- `src/games/popblast/audio.ts` — premium synthesized SFX + music bed
- `src/games/popblast/fx.ts` — particles, score popups, celebrations, screen shake
- `src/games/popblast/hud.ts` — glass HUD with animated counters
- `src/games/popblast/style.css` — Ethio Telecom premium theme
- `games/popblast/index.html` — menus, HUD, victory/game-over screens

## Instead

- Copy Candy Blast **patterns** into shared modules or other games
- Fix platform/hub/backend issues without touching Candy Blast game code
- If a shared change affects Candy Blast, **tell the user** which shared file changed and why
